@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "移民新西兰";
}

<section class="py-5 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">移民新西兰</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted">
                多种移民途径助您实现新西兰梦想：为技术人才、家庭、退休人士与投资人量身定制。
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">技术移民类别 (SMC)</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">基于积分的居留途径，适用于具备学历与经验的专业人士。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">绿名单直通车</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">针对新西兰紧缺职位，申请人可快速获批居留。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">父母团聚类别</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">新西兰公民或居民的父母可申请家庭团聚移民。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">父母退休类别</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">为经济独立、希望与子女团聚的退休人士提供居留方案。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">配偶类别</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">新西兰公民或居民的伴侣/配偶可申请居留身份。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Active Investor Plus</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">在政府认可资产中投资500万纽币以上，即可申请快速移民。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-3">不确定哪条路径最适合您？</h4>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">我们的持牌顾问将为您提供个性化评估与完整移民规划。</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">
                获取一对一专业评估
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
